snippet.title: Asphalt 9: Legends - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Take on the most fearless drivers and become the next Asphalt Legend in the best arcade racing experience for iOS, Android and Windows 10. Download now: http://gmlft.co/Asphalt9Legends

In Asphalt 9: Legends, players are able to take the wheel of the most prestigious cars across amazing real world locations. Complete hundreds of events in the solo Career mode and face up to 7 players in real time in the multiplayer mode. You can even create your own Race Club and recruit players to compete as a team to be the best in the world! 

** Stay connected **
Facebook: http://gmlft.co/A9Facebook
Twitter: https://twitter.com/asphalt 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/asphaltgames
Forum: http://gmlft.co/A9_Forum
